				<div class="ol-list-block center">
					<%= image_tag 'marketing/careers/Central-team.jpg', class: "block-image" %>
					<p class="avenir-medium">We’re responsible for the strategy and resourcing of the business, supporting the different teams in achieving their goals.</p>
